; フリーモード用シナリオ・後半




;■ムーンストーンの魔石
*kobold_6

; サファイアシティ
@saveon
@wait time=500
[texton w=1]
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00
[シュバルツ f=01]「Hey there.」[k]
As we left the inn, we ran into Schwarz, who we'd last met at the Temple of Polaris.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「How's the adventure going? Actually, I have something for you.」[k]
[name f=other_06]Saying this, Schwarz handed us a shiny jewel.[k]
[リーダー f=05]「This is...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「It is a Moonstone, one of the 12 magical stones. I talked to a friend of mine who gave it to me for free.」[k]
[name f=other_06]It was a magic stone that emitted a white light. It radiated a different kind of brilliance and magic power than the Emerald Magic Stone.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You intend to summon the god Polaris and defeat the devil, right? So of course you should have this stone.」[k]
[textoff]
@getitem item=ムーンストーンの魔石
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=01]「You guys will have to collect the remaining magic stones yourself. Good luck. See you then.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[eventoff]




;■地下の町ライムストーンに到達
*return_4

; 地下の町ライムストーン
@saveon
@wait time=1000
[texton w=0]
Passing through the narrow passageway that was the town gate, I found a huge cavern beyond, and to my surprise, a town where people lived had been built there.[k]
It's unbelievable that people live in places so deep underground...[k]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「Ah, brave adventurer. Welcome to our town!」[k]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「Thank you very much for your help in helping me. As promised, I am pleased to present you all with a gift of thanks.」[k]
[textoff]
@getitem item=特効薬
[texton w=0]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「There are many unusual things in this underground town that aren't found above ground. Please take your time to look around.」[k]
The girl left, bowing repeatedly.[k]
[textoff]
[townoff]




;■宝物庫内で悪魔と戦闘
*treasury_3

; 宝物庫内
@saveon
[texton]
We went inside the treasure chamber, but it was empty and there was nothing inside. There were no treasures to be found.[k]
According to the quest, this place was supposed to be overflowing with treasure. However, no matter how much I look around the vault, I can't see any at all.[k]
[？？？]「Hahahaha! You foolish adventurers!」[k]
Suddenly, someone behind me laughed mockingly![k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=n
@wait time=500
[texton]
We immediately turn around and prepare our weapons. Then...[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=demon_white left=450 top=-232
@wait time=500
[texton w=1]
[？？？ f=demon_00]「Kukukuku...」[k]
It certainly looked like a demon. However, compared to a typical one, its body was clearly one or two sizes larger.[k]
Could it be a high-ranking demon...?[k]
[？？？ f=demon_00]「I am Malphas.」[k]
Malphas. A high-ranking demon on par with Murmur. Why are such high-ranking demons coming to the human realm one after another...?![k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「Hah... You foolish human adventurers.」[k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「That request was made by me to lure you all here! To consume the physical strength and magical power of you adventurers and fully restore my own power!」[k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「...Hmm, everyone has decent magical powers. This should be interesting. Hehhehheh.」[k]
Malphas licks his lips as he looks at us. It seems that there is no choice but to fight.[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; マイルフィックと戦闘
@wait time=500
@eval exp='m.マイルフィック.btcmd.remove(o.死のブレス)'
@monster pos=3 name=マイルフィック
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true
@eval exp='o.古代の宝物庫.flag = 1'

[eventoff]



;■牢獄クエスト

*jail_01

; 牢獄入口
@se f=kacha
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[リーダー f=05]「...?!」[k]
[textoff]
@playse storage=acid
@image layer=e1 storage=9999 opacity=0 visible=true
@image layer=e2 storage=PE_base_full left=0 top=0 visible=true
@startemit layer=e2 storage=PE_smoke_gray time=2500
@move layer=e1 time=2000 path=,,255
@wait time=2000
[texton]
The moment we stepped on the floor of the passageway in front of the door, pure white smoke billowed out from the surrounding walls![k]
The narrow aisle quickly filled with smoke. As everyone inhaled it, they collapsed![k]
[textoff]
@black time=1000
@layopt layer=e1 visible=false
@clearemit layer=e2
@w2

[iscript]
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o.マリア.exp = o.マリア.getNeedExp(20);	// マリアのレベルを上げておく
o.マリア.levelUpToTheLast();

f.allPrisoners = [
	"看守","看守"
	,"囚人","囚人","囚人","囚人"
	,"シスター","シスター","シスター","シスター","シスター"
];
f.atrociousPrisoners = ["バジリスク", "デザートバイパー", "マンイーター"];
f.atrociousPrisoners.shuffle();

f.partyPrisonerNums = [];
for(var i = game.party.members.count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
{
	var one = game.party.members[i];
	if(i == 0) break;
	f.partyPrisonerNums.add(game.chara.find(one));
	game.party.removeMember(one);
	f.allPrisoners.add("仲間");
}

f.allPrisoners.remove("仲間", false);	// １つだけ抜いておく
while(f.allPrisoners.count < 18) f.allPrisoners.add("なし");
f.allPrisoners.shuffle();
f.partyPrisonerNums.shuffle();

game.guest.eraseHiring();	// 召喚・雇用キャラを外す
for(var i = game.guest.members.count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
{
	game.removeMemberTemporary(game.guest.members[i]);
}
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[endscript]

; ゲストを外しておく（元いた場所にいる）
@call storage="den1f.map" target=*_remove_member

; 牢屋に移動
@warp map=牢獄Ｂ２ x=7 y=5 way=s sound=false

; 先頭キャラが収監された牢屋
@black off=0
[texton]
[リーダー f=12][nw]「...! (Ah!)」[/nw][k]
When I woke up, I was in a small stone room.[k]
This is a prison. It appears that we've been captured by the enemy.[k]
This must be how the perpetrators captured all the adventurers who came to investigate. That was the reason why no one ever returned.[k]
However, remaining a prisoner forever wasn't an option. [リーダー] began to think of a way to escape.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


*jail_02

; 先頭キャラが収監された牢屋
@wait time=500
[texton]
I touch the door of the prison.[k]
The door is very sturdy, made of steel, and it is unlikely that it could be broken.[k]
The walls are made of stone and look solid, so it would take decades to even drill a hole in them.[k]
...The prison is unexpectedly strong. It may be almost impossible to escape by force.[k]
Was I destined to rot away as a prisoner...?[k]
@se f=kacha
∗slam∗[k]
Suddenly, with the sound of a key being turned, the door to the room opened slightly![k]
[textoff]
@se f=door4
@wait time=500
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=05
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va192 f=05]「Hey! Are you okay?」[k]
Surprisingly, a female adventurer opened the cell door.[k]
[マリア v=va193 f=02]「My name is Maria.」[k]
[マリア v=va194 f=02]「I'm here to help you. So get out while there are no guards nearby!」[k]
[textoff]
@black on=500
@wait time=500
@warp x=6 y=3 way=w sound=false
@fgf c=マリア f=02
@black off=500
[texton]
[マリア v=va195 f=02]「Hey, that was a disaster.」[k]
[リーダー] asked her why she had come to help them.[k]
[マリア v=va196 f=14]「Well... Actually, the client for your quest is me.」[k]
[マリア v=va197 f=02]「...As I'm sure you've heard, this quest was attempted by several parties of adventurers. They all disappeared without being able to solve it.」[k]
[マリア v=va198 f=02]「The client was at a loss as to why.」[k]
[マリア v=va199 f=02]「So, I decided to find out why adventurers keep disappearing in this prison and then launch a full-scale rescue operation.」[k]
[マリア v=va200 f=02]「I was consulted by the client about this matter before you guys.」[k]
[マリア v=va201 f=02]「After much deliberation, we decided to have someone else take on this request and observe how the enemy catches adventurers who try to infiltrate.」[k]
[マリア v=va202 f=02]「Then you guys took up the offer and I followed you to the prison.」[k]
[マリア v=va203 f=02]「I watched from a distance as you infiltrated this prison.」[k]
[マリア v=va204 f=02]「After finding out about that immobilization trap at the entrance, I was able to sneak in without being caught by the enemy.」[k]
...Apparently, the party was used as bait.[k]
[マリア v=va205 f=53]「Sorry! But I was going to get you guys out of there right away and have you do the rescue mission with me! I'm pretty good at picking locks.」[k]
[マリア f=06]「...」[k]
Maria suddenly falls silent, as if she has something on her mind.[k]
[マリア v=va207 f=09]「The cell doors here are much sturdier than I thought they would be. It would take a long time to pry them open. Your cell happened to have a simple lock, so I was able to open it...」[k]
[マリア v=va208 f=09]「Given time I could pick the other ones, but if it's too slow, the guards would find out. I'd like to get the [b]prison key[/b] if possible. The guards should have it...」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.マリア)'
@st
@se f=up3
@notice text="<y>Maria joined the party!"
@mu f=&'game.map.bgm'
[eventoff]


; *jail_05

; 監獄の外
@wait time=500
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'
@fg c=マリア f=00
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va218 f=02]「Well, that's it for me. Thanks for your help, everyone.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
@addevent map=ブルーのアジト１Ｆ num=9
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>Maria left the party.<r>Guests who left have returned."
[eventoff]



;■ラブホ売春組織壊滅クエスト

; ラブホで売春組織が暗躍している
; 主人公たちはラブホに一般のカップルのふりをして潜入し事件を解決する

*hotel_1

; ホテルの前
@saveon
@bg f=0037
@w05
[texton w=1]
[リーダー f=06]「This is the love hotel the quest mentioned...」[k]
We arrived in front of Hotel Queen. Is prostitution taking place here?[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=01
[サンドラ v=vn042 f=01]「The security team asked me to help everyone. I'm Sandra. Nice to meet you.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn044 f=01]「Actually, I used to work at this hotel.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn061 f=08]「That hotel has a secret passageway underground for members only, and they arrange prostitution there. If we catch them in the act, we can expose the reality of prostitution.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn063 f=08]「The secret passage can only be accessed from inside the hotel, so tonight, pretend to be a normal couple when you check in, and then wait in your room.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn064 f=08]「Meet at the designated place at midnight. Got it?」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=coin
@getitem gold=10000

; 予約画面へ
@out
@gameon
@addevent name=ホテル・クイーン num=1
[iscript]
game.exitTravelMode();
game.innActionCount = 0;
game.openHotelView(o.ホテル・クイーン);
game.hotelView.exitButton.visible = false;
game.hotelView.sleepNowButton.visible = false;
game.hotelView.reserveRoom(, game.hotelView.getRoomFromRoomName("従業員通路"));
game.hotelView.checkEarlyEvent();
[endscript]
[s]


*hotel_5

; ホテル内・夜
[iscript]
game.hour = "night";
game.hotelView.openRoamingMap(o.ホテル・クイーン);
game.hotelView.sleepButton.visible = false;
game.innActionCount = 1;
for(var i = 0; i < game.hotelView.visMarkers.count; i++)
{
	if(! game.hotelView.visMarkers[i].visible) continue;
	game.hotelView.visMarkers[i].selectable = false;
}
game.hotelView.getRoomFromRoomName("従業員通路").clear();
[endscript]
@addeventbtn map=ホテル・クイーン label=隠し通路_1 name=隠し通路 img=sandra x=900 y=200
[hoteloff]


*hotel_6

; 夜のホテルの隠し通路
@saveon
@bg f=0040
@fg c=サンドラ e=戦闘 f=02
[texton w=1]
[サンドラ v=vn065 f=02]「Here you are.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn135 f=05]「Well then, let's go inside.」[k]
[textoff]
@out

[iscript]
game.hour = "day";
f.checkinList = game.hotelView.store();
for(var i = 0; i < game.party.members.count; i++)
{
	game.party.members[i].storeAllItemsInOthers(game.temporaryBox);
	game.party.members[i].dressEquipment(o.バスタオル,,, true);
	game.party.members[i].makeBustups();
}
if(game.guest.getHiring() !== void)
{
	var hire = game.guest.getHiring();
	hire.equipLife = G_TOWELF;
	hire.makeBustups();
}
game.guest.entry(o.サンドラ);
game.inEvent = false;
game.townView.close();
game.loadDungeonAtBackGround(%[map:"ホテルの地下Ｂ１", x:11, y:3, way:"s"]);
[endscript]
[eventoff]


*hotel_7

; ホテル内・敵事務所
@wait time=500
@fg l=thief_red left=340 top=80 b
@fgf r=thief_red left=560 top=80
[texton w=1]
[name n="Organization Executive"]「W-who the hell are you?」[k]
When I entered the room, there were a large number of girls and several men who appeared to be senior members of the organization hanging around.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn068 f=07]「I know you're making money by forcing lots of girls into prostitution! I'll turn you over to the security guards, so just give up and let them arrest you!」[k]
[name n="Organization Executive"]「What the hell?」[k]
[name n="Organization Executive"]「You idiots! Who would get caught by you guys? Hey, you bastards! Take them down!」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; 組織幹部と戦闘
@monster pos=1 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=2 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=3 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=4 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=5 name=ハイウェイマン
@monster pos=9 name=ブッシュワッカー
@monster pos=10 name=バーグラー
@monster pos=11 name=ブッシュワッカー
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true
; 勝利

@wait time=500
[texton w=0]
After defeating the members of the organization, we managed to capture them all. We handed them over to the security guards who arrived later.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn069 f=01]「Leave the rest to the security guards, and let's go outside.」[k]
[textoff]
@out t=1000
@wait time=500



; ホテルの外
@bg f=0039
[texton w=0]
We handed over the captured members of the organization to the town guards and left the hotel.[k]
The girls who had been forced into prostitution were all freed, and the case was provisionally settled.[k]
[警備隊長]「Thanks to you guys, I was able to destroy the organization. Thank you so much.」[k]
[警備隊長]「Please accept your reward. If anything else comes up, I'll count on you again.」[k]
[textoff]

@eval exp='o.売春組織の実体を暴け.exp += f.rescuedGirls * 10000'
@eval exp='o.売春組織の実体を暴け.gold += f.rescuedGirls * 5000'
@complete name=売春組織の実体を暴け
@addevent name=ホテル・クイーン num=6

@fg c=サンドラ f=01
[texton w=1]
[サンドラ v=vn070 f=01]「Thank you for your help this time. Let's go on another adventure together when we have the chance.」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.サンドラ)'
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>Sandra left the party."
; ブルーのアジトに待機させる
@addevent map=ブルーのアジト１Ｆ num=8
@changefloor map=ブルーのアジト１Ｆ x=6 y=0 pimg=human

@eval exp='game.enterTown(o.サファイアシティ, o.ホテル・クイーン, true)'
