;■全てを見通せる鏡

*mirror_1

; アイテム画面から千里の鏡を使用直後
@out
@bg f=9008
@w05
[texton w=1]
When I touched the crystal on the top frame of the Mirror of 1000 Miles, the mirror surface suddenly brightened, and something else was reflected in it.[k]
Something resembling text is reflected in the mirror. It appears to be instructions on how to use the mirror.[k]
The description stated that this mirror could reflect any distant location, and that the only places that could be viewed were those that the mirror had been taken to and "registered".[k]
Looking further at the mirror, there was already some information about places that have been registered by someone. The mechanism is such that when you touch them, the places you want to see are displayed.[k]
I decided to try touching one of them.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@bg f=event91
@w1
[texton w=1]
Surprisingly, a location that appears to be a bathroom was reflected in the mirror![k]
What's more... there was a naked woman there. Could this be the bar mistress from the tavern in Limestone Town?[k]
On the screen, the naked mistress is seen washing her body, unaware that she is being watched.[k]
It was a view from quite close up, and I could clearly see her body.[k]
What kind of places did the  previous owner register?! This isn't fit to be shown to anyone.[k]
Fortunately, it seems that the location registration information can be "deleted". Once deleted, it will no longer be possible to view this bathroom.[k]
[textoff]

@gameon
[texton w=0]
The previous owner's registration information was then deleted from the Mirror of 1000 Miles. Now it can be handed over to the client with peace of mind.[k]
[textoff]
@se f=period
@eval exp='o.全てを見通せる鏡.flag = 1'
@return




;■教団壊滅クエスト

*fortress
; 森の要塞４Ｆ・謁見の間
@saveon
@w05
[if exp='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)']
	@bg f=event100 p0=02
	@w05
	[texton w=2]
	[マリア v=va221 e=裸 f=37]「Ah... Ah... Ah... Ah...」[k]
	[name n=Guru]「Hmm, what a wonderful vagina. This feels very good.」[k]
	This was the audience chamber. It was a place where the founder of this religious cult would receive visitors, and also a room where he indulged in pleasure.[k]
	In the center was his throne. Surrounding it were a dozen or so women who appeared to be his attendants. They were all naked.[k]
	And on the floor in the center of the room, Maria lay naked on her back.[k]
	She was being raped by the half-naked cult leader.[k]
	Maria does not resist. Perhaps her consciousness is clouded, as she stares blankly into space with glazed eyes.[k]
	She spread her legs languidly and silently accepted the man's actions.[k]
	[マリア v=va222 f=37]「Ah... Ah... Ah... Ah...」[k]
	[name n=Guru]「Daughter, you will become my follower. And you will continue to serve me sexually. Do you understand?」[k]
	[マリア v=va228 f=39]「...Yes.」[k]
	With a vacant look in her eyes, Maria nodded quietly.[k]
	[textoff]
	@out
	@w05
[endif]
@gameon
[texton w=1]
We threw open the door and stormed into the audience chamber![k]
It was a large hall, and there were a dozen or so naked women standing around the edges of the room.[k]
In the center was a man dressed in a magnificent robe.[if exp='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)'] Surprisingly, Maria was there too.[k]
What's more, Maria was naked and being raped by the man in the robe.[endif][k]
[name n=Guru f=rich_00]「What's going on? Has someone arrived?」[k]
The man noticed us and hurriedly stood up.[k]
[name n=Guru f=rich_00]「W-who are all of you?」[k]
[if exp='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)'][マリア e=裸 f=98]「...」[k][endif]
The arrest warrant issued by the Sapphire City Guard we received from the guild is presented to the panicked cult leader.[k]
[name n=Guru f=rich_00]「Adventurers...! You bastards from Sapphire City are interfering with my plans! Everyone! Gather around!」[k]
When the guru gave the order, all the naked female followers around us grabbed their weapons and stood before us![k]
[name n=Guru f=rich_00]「I will not let mere adventurers destroy my sect! Expel this infidel, my devout followers!」[k]
The cult leader and his followers attacked us![k]
[textoff]
@clf

