@monster pos=2 naked=2 name=デュエリスト
@monster pos=3 naked=2 name=デュエリスト
@monster pos=4 naked=2 name=デュエリスト
@monster pos=5 naked=2 name=デュエリスト
@monster pos=8 naked=2 name=マスターランサー
@monster pos=10 naked=2 name=マスターランサー
@monster pos=12 naked=2 name=マスターランサー
@monster pos=16 naked=2 name=メイガス
@monster pos=17 name=教祖
@monster pos=18 naked=2 name=メイガス
@callbattle bgm=boss gameover=true
; 勝利

[texton w=0]
[name n=Guru f=rich_00]「Damn you...!」[k]
We defeated the cult leader and took him into custody.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@gameon
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=14 cond='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)'
[texton w=1]
[if exp='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)']
	[マリア v=va229 f=14]「I made a big mistake... If you all hadn't come, I wonder what would have happened...」[k]
	Maria, having regained her sanity, spoke of her failure with self-deprecating humor.[k]
	It turned out that Maria had also accepted that request and infiltrated the cult's facility ahead of us.[k]
	However, she was captured by the enemy and hypnotized by the cult leader. That is why she was unable to resist.[k]
[endif]
@fgf c=マリア f=01
[マリア v=va230 f=01]「That cult leader seems to have lured young people with sweet talk and brainwashed them with hypnosis to become his followers. But now we can bring everyone back to their senses.」[k]
We then handed the guru over to the guards from Sapphire City who followed behind us, and left the cult facility.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>We destroyed the cult!"
@eval exp='o.教団を壊滅させろ.flag = 2'
[if exp='! game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)']
