;■山小屋パブでの会話

*event_山小屋パブ_3

@wait time=500
[texton]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「Oh, do you have a magic stone by any chance?」[k]
As we took our seats, a nearby middle-aged woman spoke to us.[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「I had one too, so I know all about them.」[k]
That's unexpected. If the story is true, is it possible to get or borrow it from her?[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「What? You're collecting magic stones?」[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「Unfortunately, I lost it. A few months ago.」[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「I used to wear that [b]Opal Magic Stone[/b] all the time, but then I dropped it.」[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「When I entered the open-air bath at the hot spring, I slipped and fell.」[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「Then the magic stone came off and rolled out of the open-air bath... right over a steep cliff next to it!」[k]
We asked what happened to the magic stone after that.[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「I gave up, since it fell somewhere I'd never be able to get to. Maybe the magic stone is still there.」[k]
What a resigned woman. She doesn't seem to understand how precious the stone is.[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「[b]Yanek Hot Springs[/b] is where it was. The Opal Magic Stone fell down the cliff outside the [b]women's open-air bath[/b].」[k]
[name n="Middle-aged woman"]「Honestly, I think it's going to be pretty hard to find that thing, so good luck with that. I don't need it anymore, so if you can find it, it's yours.」[k]
[textoff]
[baroff]




*jail_05

; 監獄の外
@wait time=500

; サンドラが仲間だった場合
[if exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.サンドラ)']
	@fg c=サンドラ f=05
	[texton w=1]
	[サンドラ v=vn038 f=05]「Oh, there you are. Honestly, I was so worried.」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Sandra was waiting for us. Apparently, she was safe.[k]
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Sandra rejoined the party!"
[endif]

; ミレディが仲間だった場合
[if exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.ミレディ)']
	@fg c=ミレディ f=01
	[texton w=1]
	[ミレディ v=vm182 f=01]「Ahh! There you are! You're safe～!」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Miredy was waiting for us. Apparently, she was safe.[k]
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Miredy rejoined the party!"
[endif]

; ポラリスが仲間だった場合
[if exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.ポラリス)']
	@fg c=ポラリス f=01
	[texton w=1]
	[ポラリス v=vp031 f=01]「We were very worried. I am glad to hear that everyone is safe.」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Lady Polaris was waiting for us. Apparently, she was safe.[k]
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Polaris rejoined the party!"
[endif]

; 監獄の外
@wait time=500
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'
@fg c=マリア f=00
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va218 f=02]「Well, that's it for me. Thanks for your help, everyone.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
